            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic in pace q<supplied reason="lost">uie</supplied>scunt benidictus <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/><expan><ex>d</ex><abbr>iacon</abbr></expan>&amp;lt;u=I&amp;gt;s Bes<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>ntio et neptis sua <lb n="3"/>benedicta pu<supplied reason="lost">ell</supplied>a Iusticiola <lb n="4"/>obiit Iustic<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>ola puella VIII <expan><abbr>Ka</abbr><ex>lendas</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>et <expan><ex>d</ex><abbr>iacon</abbr></expan>&amp;lt;u=I&amp;gt;s Besontio VII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Apri</abbr><ex>les</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei nicht aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Platte, mittig ausgebessert. Oberhalb der Inschrift Christogramm, flankiert von Tauben, über den Tauben lateinische Kreuze (Ritzzeichnungen). (B): Nikitsch; Terrien; Binsfeld: Abweichungen in Lesung/Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
